translate indonesian christie_root_24_cf5a83ae:
    # "You're back!"
    "Kau kembali!"

translate indonesian christie_root_24_a4d3de23:
    # "I knew you would."
    "Aku tahu kau akan kembali."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_f0587e9c:
    # mc "Yeah? How?"
    mc "Ya? Bagaimana kau tahu?"

translate indonesian christie_root_24_0168b1ff:
    # "They all come back, he-heh-heh."
    "Mereka semua kembali, he-heh-heh."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_07ba41b1:
    # mc "Ha-ha. You're very friendly."
    mc "Ha-ha. Kau ramah sekali."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_395b379e:
    # "It's probably because I love getting compliments."
    "Mungkin karena aku suka menerima pujian."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_dcd8e659:
    # mc "Oh, I've got plenty of those. I don't mind giving some to you."
    mc "Oh, aku punya banyak pujian. Aku tidak keberatan memberikannya padamu."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_512d022c:
    # "He-he-heh."
    "He-he-heh."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_970107a4:
    # mc "Can I go to the reading room and get the same «Social Studies» books from you?"
    mc "Boleh aku pergi ke ruang baca dan mendapatkan buku «Ilmu Sosial» yang sama darimu?"

translate indonesian christie_root_24_fad209d8:
    # "Of course."
    "Tentu saja."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_f3af5c41:
    # mc "A few words about that, a few words about this..."
    mc "Beberapa kata tentang itu, beberapa kata tentang ini..."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_1c25ba08:
    # mc "Analytical calculations, statistics, public reaction to it."
    mc "Perhitungan analitis, statistik, reaksi publik terhadapnya."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_d0bcab58:
    # mc "A paragraph, another paragraph, a note of importance... Well, that should do it for today."
    mc "Satu paragraf, paragraf lain, catatan penting... Yah, sepertinya cukup untuk hari ini."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_3fd09947:
    # mc "I think I'm almost done..."
    mc "Kurasa aku hampir selesai..."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_ff612eb9:
    # mc "The main thing is not to forget to mention the basics of cultural studies and the problems of subjective presentation, but I'll deal with that next time."
    mc "Yang penting jangan lupa menyebutkan dasar-dasar kajian budaya dan masalah penyajian subjektif, tapi akan kuurus itu lain kali."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_d7f6c613:
    # mc "At the moment, I'm completely exhausted and I don't want to think about it anymore."
    mc "Saat ini aku benar-benar kelelahan dan tidak ingin memikirkannya lagi."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_bfe3d0cd:
    # "Do you always work till late night?"
    "Apa kau selalu bekerja sampai larut malam?"

translate indonesian christie_root_24_593a2564:
    # mc "Heh... My life has taken a sharp turn lately, and me doing this kind of job is probably just a side effect of all that."
    mc "Heh... Hidupku belakangan ini berubah drastis, dan pekerjaan seperti ini mungkin hanya efek samping dari semua itu."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_2cb27dc5:
    # "You take care of yourself."
    "Jaga dirimu baik-baik."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_26cd9e55:
    # "The library is a house of knowledge, not a graveyard of workaholics."
    "Perpustakaan adalah rumah pengetahuan, bukan kuburan para workaholic."

translate indonesian christie_root_24_356d6e27:
    # mc "Thanks for your advice. I'll try to stay alive."
    mc "Terima kasih atas nasihatmu. Aku akan berusaha tetap hidup."

translate indonesian strings:
    old "1. Отправиться в библиотеку и продолжить написание реферата по теме «Обществознание» (2/3)."
    new "1. Pergi ke perpustakaan pada Pagi atau Siang untuk melanjutkan esai Ilmu Sosial. (2/3)."
